{"tid":1698141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警稱有人假冒鄧炳強　向政府部門發「含侮辱性字句」電郵","createTime":"2019-11-07T09:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T01:32:25.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ab5769979001061fa10f5bedd38590b9d139298d","tid":1698141,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:51:55.000Z","msg":"警方表示，昨（6日）接獲相關政府部門報案，稱有人假冒警務處副處長向政府部門發出偽冒電郵，內含侮辱性字句，案件交網絡安全及科技罪案調查科跟進。據了解，涉事者是假冒警務處副處長（行動）鄧炳強發出有關電郵。<br />\n<br />\n警方澄清，警務處副處長並沒有發出該虛假電郵；強烈譴責涉案者，並提醒市民勿以身試法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191107/s00001/1573118607817/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191107%2Fs00001%2F1573118607817%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=5ce09cf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191107%2Fs00001%2F1573118607817%2F&h=c9fc45c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191107/s00001/1573118607817/</a>"},{"pid":"748a96a5f18f7d02c616d2aff1aaaf03e2d570c1","tid":1698141,"uid":68689,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"黑警又作case"},{"pid":"cebbbd18e33fe0a3a2c8778be53eeba844a9d326","tid":1698141,"uid":36065,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:53:44.000Z","msg":"仲邊有人信"},{"pid":"585255060817b58217871c0ae6e9e03d021c3e0d","tid":1698141,"uid":51271,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:55:06.000Z","msg":"點證實係假"},{"pid":"77a9a9539e3e2cd7c4b4076532191c9d840b7a6f","tid":1698141,"uid":256246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"咁啱呀，阿邊個又話係俾人hack改facebook出feed時間wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397265e6f3329abd6e914980ffd6fe4623149f24","t